version_description: Very upbeat, it's best to use bar chords. Listen and play along to figure out the feel of the strumming pattern: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XInQG60o0PM.
Sounds okay, but I tabbed it by ear, so a couple of chords might not be entirely correct.
I used the correct chords and you can play along with the song.

You can mimic the sound of song better if you play the first verse mostly with the root notes and some palm muting, then open up the chords at the start of the second verse. Play along to get the feel for it: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B3H3whbsaX8.
